{"tid":706542,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 世界盃新學問 如何正確撓手","createTime":"2018-06-18T03:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T13:13:39.000Z","uid":54079,"like":1037,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"d69a382f9b3555a477bd9998999566730860572a","tid":706542,"uid":54079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"世界盃賽場無輪輸贏，32支球隊的每位球員都有一必須完成的指定動作。電視觀眾在每場開賽前，都會在電視看到對賽球隊的球員簡介短片，他們都會不約而同做簡單招牌動作：轉身撓手。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n看起來類似的動作還是有細微差異，有評論覺得像日本球員內田篤人做得不錯，但美國的碧卡文似乎在影疑犯照。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2014/07/a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2014%2F07%2Fa.gif&h=4fa9bf31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關鍵是手應該放在哪裡，像荷蘭隊的真馬特將手放在「老鼠仔」外還是像墨西哥守門員奧祖亞，將手插進手臂再豎起大拇指？<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2014/07/b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2014%2F07%2Fb.gif&h=c126b8d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但不管怎麼放，千萬別像哥倫比亞三位球員一樣把手放在腋下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2014/07/70753781gw1ei3grx5h54g20dc05ke81.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2014%2F07%2F70753781gw1ei3grx5h54g20dc05ke81.gif&h=e581d500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下三位球員又提醒大家另一個需要注意的地方：如何左轉？是像一個對孩子不滿的爸爸(伊朗球員尼古納姆)？還是像一隻受驚的兔子(克羅地亞隊摩迪歷)？跟厄瓜多爾隊謝法臣蒙迪路一樣像個機器人？還是像經過長期治療以後擁抱自己(加納隊卡華禾艾沙姆)？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2014/07/c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2014%2F07%2Fc.gif&h=0d8cb84c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於轉速問題，轉太快就是阿爾及利亞門將麥保希的效果；再慢點就是尼日利亞中場奧根耶奧拿斯這樣了；再慢下去就是喀麥隆隊謝迪祖一樣，鏡頭一晃過去臂還是抱不到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2014/07/70753781gw1ei3gtlbcc6g20dc05kb29.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2014%2F07%2F70753781gw1ei3gtlbcc6g20dc05kb29.gif&h=8da06699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果速度剛好，效果會很有魔力。像英格蘭門神的祖赫特思考人生的憂鬱小眼神，姿勢擺出來猶如樂隊裡明星，還有阿爾及利亞的麥贊尼引人注目的剔眉直情想望穿屏幕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2014/07/70753781gw1ei3gu07afhg20dc08cu0x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2014%2F07%2F70753781gw1ei3gu07afhg20dc08cu0x.gif&h=0f4e6028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在所有球員中，撓手冠亞軍當屬喀麥隆的伊高圖，以及荷蘭的洛賓。前者將優雅、有趣和輕鬆融為一體；後者撓手動作和他球場上一樣瀟灑利落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2014/07/70753781gw1ei3gutl4gig208w0b4npd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2014%2F07%2F70753781gw1ei3gutl4gig208w0b4npd.gif&h=708a807c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2014/07/70753781gw1ei3guh092mg208w0b4npd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2014%2F07%2F70753781gw1ei3guh092mg208w0b4npd.gif&h=484b609e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/261976-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83%E6%96%B0%E5%AD%B8%E5%95%8F-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E6%92%93%E6%89%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F261976-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%259B%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2595%258F-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E6%2592%2593%25E6%2589%258B&d=PG4Oxvt61KFSqZ%2F8SnozV49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8814676e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/261976-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83%E6%96%B0%E5%AD%B8%E5%95%8F-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E6%92%93%E6%89%8B</a>"},{"pid":"2286b751592e838363aa0d69c5ad4969aa274d08","tid":706542,"uid":54079,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6179876f3610fdfc0529f756ebf68f1e04a0d4","tid":706542,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda2078cca17566ba3a11694407c212e7e203762","tid":706542,"uid":36054,"like":488,"dislike":1,"score":487,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"轉太快太慢果個笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe99073365e77328090bb29b10fb880755d6660","tid":706542,"uid":117802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1ba1cf862fda607e7d079975aca05d4a034642","tid":706542,"uid":167157,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"洛賓好有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a33473ff781f6c919ae43e5a42052bfba5af40b","tid":706542,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:31:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1efc216fc2d8451c8ca516d29c0c14167555d5ee","tid":706542,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55354dee058b651c64706cea3da51369694fda6c","tid":706542,"uid":16256,"like":0,"disl